title: Lilium Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual cafe making sandwiches, burgers, wraps, green smoothies, and coffee. Has a vegetarian lentil burger, pumpkin wrap, falafel wrap w/cheese and hummus. Vegans to specify or build-your-own salad or sandwich. Aug 2014 reported changed ownership, previously Simply Sandwiches.
